### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/api/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Query — Ask a question
POST http://localhost:8000/api/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What happened during World War II?"
}

###

### Ingest File — Upload a file
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ingest/file
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="history.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

< ../resources/history.txt
------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="strategy"

fixed
------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="split_method"

fixed_size
------boundary--

###

### Ingest Directory — Ingest from local path
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ingest/directory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": "resources/",
  "recursive": true,
  "strategy": "fixed",
  "split_method": "fixed_size"
}

###

### Ingest Directory — Parent-child with title splitting
POST http://localhost:8000/api/ingest/directory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "path": "resources/",
  "recursive": true,
  "strategy": "parent_child",
  "split_method": "title"
}
